### Get Anonymous Token
POST http://localhost:12001/api/auth/anonymous-token
Content-Type: application/json

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:12001/api/auth/health

### Test Properties API without token (should work - no auth required currently)
GET http://localhost:12001/api/properties/filters

### Get token and use it (demonstrates how frontend would work)
POST http://localhost:12001/api/auth/anonymous-token
Content-Type: application/json

> {%
  client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token);
%}

### Use the token in subsequent requests
GET http://localhost:12001/api/properties/filters
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Test property search with token
POST http://localhost:12001/api/properties/search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "region": "Hong Kong Island",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 5
}